---
layout: layout.njk
title: "Pending Guidance"
permalink: "/pending-guidance/"
---

<div class="pending-guidance-intro">
  <p>These topics require additional guidance that is currently being developed. Each item represents a request for clarification that will be addressed in future updates.</p>
</div>

<div class="pending-guidance-index">
  {% for item in pendingGuidance %}
    <div class="pending-guidance-item">
      <a href="/pending-guidance/{{ item.filename | replace('.md', '') }}/" class="pending-guidance-link">
        <div class="pending-guidance-status">
          <strong>{{ item.status or 'ðŸ›‘ Pending Guidance' }}</strong>
        </div>
        <h3 class="pending-guidance-title">{{ item.title }}</h3>
        {% if item.content or item.answer %}
          <p class="pending-guidance-preview">{{ (item.content or item.answer) | markdown | striptags | truncate(150) }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        {% if item.relatedFaqs and item.relatedFaqs.length > 0 %}
          <div class="related-count">{{ item.relatedFaqs.length }} related FAQ{{ 's' if item.relatedFaqs.length != 1 }}</div>
        {% endif %}
      </a>
    </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>